{
  "title": "Lifecycle HUD + Dashboard — Hi-Fi Mocks",
  "subtitle": "Three views of the same data: Footer (domain), HUD (lifecycle), Dashboard (expanded)",
  "theme": {"preset": "teal-slate"},
  "layout": "sidebar-toc",
  "effects": ["grid-dots", "noise"],
  "sections": [
    {
      "type": "section",
      "title": "1. The HUD (Always-On Status Bar)",
      "variant": "default",
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "content": "One line. Every response. The collapsed lifecycle state."
        },
        {
          "type": "code-block",
          "language": "text",
          "content": "🧬 lifecycle-engine ⚡0 📥0 ⏸️0 ✅32 | 🚦convergence=0.94 | ⏭️ SessionStart hook | 🔁ll:t5 270s"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "content": "**Symbol key:** 🧬 workstream | ⚡ executing | 📥 capturing | ⏸️ paused | ✅ done | 🚦 gate=score | ⏭️ next action | 🔁 loop state"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "content": "**When to show:** Every /ll tick, /work response, /exec result, /capture sweep. Lifecycle-aware skills declare `output_template: hud` in frontmatter."
        },
        {
          "type": "card",
          "title": "Design Principle",
          "content": "The HUD is a terminal status bar, not a footer. It persists across responses. It's the minimum viable context for 'where am I in the lifecycle?' One glance, one line, zero scroll."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "section",
      "title": "2. The Footer (Domain Skill Output)",
      "variant": "default",
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "content": "Multi-line block for domain skills (/interview, /tribunal, /cdo, /now). Shows skill-specific context, not lifecycle state."
        },
        {
          "type": "code-block",
          "language": "markdown",
          "content": "---\n🧬 lifecycle-engine | 📐 dna/standards×6, gate-evaluator | 🎯 Exec\n⏭️  Next: /exec (gate formulas → evaluator)\n🚦 Gate: convergence = 0.94\n🌀 Decision: execute\n---\n\nShape:   /research  /prior-art  /interview\nPlan:    /propose   /capture\nExec:    /exec      /manifest\nClose:   /qa  /accept  /handoff\nRouter:  /work"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "content": "**When to show:** Domain skills that don't track lifecycle state. Skills declare `output_template: footer` in frontmatter. Shows verb reference for navigation."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "section",
      "title": "3. The Dashboard (/siterep expanded)",
      "variant": "default",
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "content": "Full expanded view. Shows every entity, its mode, gate scores, decisions needed. This is /siterep."
        },
        {
          "type": "section",
          "title": "Active Entities",
          "variant": "kpi-row",
          "children": [
            {"type": "card", "title": "Executing", "content": "0"},
            {"type": "card", "title": "Capturing", "content": "0"},
            {"type": "card", "title": "Paused", "content": "2"},
            {"type": "card", "title": "Done", "content": "32"},
            {"type": "card", "title": "Convergence", "content": "94%"}
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "data-table",
          "title": "Entity Status",
          "columns": [
            {"key": "mode", "label": "Mode"},
            {"key": "entity", "label": "Entity"},
            {"key": "gate", "label": "Gate"},
            {"key": "score", "label": "Score"},
            {"key": "next", "label": "Next Action"}
          ],
          "rows": [
            {"mode": "⏸️", "entity": "SDLC auto-dispatch hook", "gate": "frame_complete", "score": "0.85", "next": "SessionStart hook (Step 3)"},
            {"mode": "⏸️", "entity": "TOON impl → token-compress", "gate": "frame_complete", "score": "0.70", "next": "Wire toonformat.dev Rust crate"},
            {"mode": "✅", "entity": "Gate formulas → evaluator", "gate": "convergence", "score": "PASS", "next": "Done (tick 1)"},
            {"mode": "✅", "entity": "flow.schema.yaml", "gate": "convergence", "score": "PASS", "next": "Done (tick 2)"},
            {"mode": "✅", "entity": "core-sdlc → sdlc merge", "gate": "convergence", "score": "PASS", "next": "Done (batch 1)"},
            {"mode": "✅", "entity": "Plugin invariant sweep", "gate": "convergence", "score": "PASS", "next": "Done (batch 1)"},
            {"mode": "✅", "entity": "lifecycle-manifest.yaml", "gate": "convergence", "score": "PASS", "next": "Done (batch 1)"},
            {"mode": "✅", "entity": "/work rewrite as router", "gate": "convergence", "score": "PASS", "next": "Done (tick 3)"},
            {"mode": "✅", "entity": "/propose skill created", "gate": "convergence", "score": "PASS", "next": "Done (tick 3)"},
            {"mode": "✅", "entity": "lifecycle-scanner.ts", "gate": "convergence", "score": "PASS", "next": "Done (tick 4)"}
          ]
        }
