      "title": "Session Artifacts",
      "variant": "default",
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "data-table",
          "title": "Files Created This Session",
          "columns": [
            {"key": "file", "label": "File"},
            {"key": "type", "label": "Type"},
            {"key": "lines", "label": "LOC"}
          ],
          "rows": [
            {"file": "dna/standards/agentic-search.yaml", "type": "standard", "lines": "120"},
            {"file": "dna/standards/escalation.yaml", "type": "standard", "lines": "100"},
            {"file": "dna/standards/agentic-ux.yaml", "type": "standard", "lines": "180"},
            {"file": "dna/standards/metrics.yaml", "type": "standard", "lines": "140"},
            {"file": "dna/standards/idle-exec-policy.yaml", "type": "standard", "lines": "110"},
            {"file": "dna/standards/ux-drift-detection.yaml", "type": "standard", "lines": "110"},
            {"file": "core/flowmind/src/gate-evaluator.ts", "type": "code", "lines": "+147"},
            {"file": "core/flowmind/schemas/flow.schema.yaml", "type": "schema", "lines": "150"},
            {"file": "core/flowmind/system/lifecycle-manifest.yaml", "type": "manifest", "lines": "95"},
            {"file": "plugins/sdlc/src/handlers/lifecycle-scanner.ts", "type": "code", "lines": "157"},
            {"file": "5 plugin configs", "type": "config", "lines": "+165"},
            {"file": "6 proposals", "type": "proposal", "lines": "~500"},
            {"file": "2 audit reports", "type": "report", "lines": "~100"},
            {"file": "3 skills (siterep, propose, ll)", "type": "skill", "lines": "~250"}
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "section",
      "title": "Architecture: Streaming Data into Views",
      "variant": "default",
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "content": "The dashboard reads from workstream durable artifacts. Every /capture, /exec, /ll tick writes structured YAML to `.lev/pm/workstreams/<ws>/captures/`. The dashboard projects this data."
        },
        {
          "type": "timeline",
          "title": "Data Flow: Loop → Artifact → Dashboard",
          "items": [
            {"date": "1", "title": "/ll tick fires", "description": "Lifecycle scanner reads .lev/tasks/*/dna.yaml, evaluates gates"},
            {"date": "2", "title": "Gate scores cached", "description": "Written to .lev/state/gate-scores.yaml (invalidated on file change)"},
            {"date": "3", "title": "Durable capture written", "description": "YAML report at .lev/pm/workstreams/<ws>/captures/YYYYMMDD.yaml"},
            {"date": "4", "title": "Dashboard reads artifacts", "description": "/siterep or /lev renders from cached state — no re-computation"},
            {"date": "5", "title": "Auto-hygiene on attach", "description": "When workstream artifacts are attached, lifecycle events scan for drift"}
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "card",
          "title": "Promotion Pathway",
          "content": "Ephemeral (.lev/.cache/) → Scratch (.lev/.scratch/) → Proposal (.lev/pm/proposals/) → DNA (dna/) or Docs (docs/). Config-driven: .lev/config.yaml declares which paths auto-promote."
        },
        {
          "type": "card",
          "title": "Websocket Streaming (future)",
          "content": "For live dashboards: gate-scores.yaml changes → SSE/WS push → browser auto-refreshes. Current: meta.refresh on /now pages (polling). Future: reactive FS watch → event stream."
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
